pages.text: How to Schedule a Tee Time For two or more golfers: please book your tee time online using the button below. Schedule a Tee Time For single golfers: please call the Pro Shop at 850-891-2540 to book your tee time over the phone. Due to availability, you might be paired with other golfers to complete a group. This can be a great opportunity to meet fellow golf enthusiasts! When calling, feel free to share any specific preferences or questions you may have. We're here to help ensure you have an enjoyable experience on the course. History of Jake Gaither Read the History of Jake Gaither. Course Details Course Play Hours: 7:30 a.m. - Sunset Pro Shop Hours: Spring/Summer During Daylight Saving Time 7:30 a.m. - 6 p.m. Fall/Winter During Standard Time 7:30 a.m. - 5 p.m. (Course and Pro Shop are open 7 Days a Week, but Closed Thanksgiving Day and Christmas Day) 801 Bragg Drive • 850-891-3942 The Jake Gaither Golf Course is a nine-hole, par 36 with a course/slope rating of 69.8/127. The course offers a pro shop with golf merchandise and snack items, a practice putting green, and rental clubs. The entire course was renovated in 1998 and the additional tee areas make the course very enjoyable for all level of golfers. Upcoming Events Irene Perry Invitational Tournament Thursday, September 18, 8:00 AM – Thursday, September 18, 1:00 PM Contact: Linda Inage Phone Number: 850-933-9991 8 a.m. Shotgun Start ––– JLB Championship Saturday, September 27, 9:00 AM – Saturday, September 27, 1:00 PM Contact: Tiant DeWindt Shotgun Start at 9 a.m. Phone Number: 850-891-2539 Register ––– Rental Space Rental space is available at the Jake Gaither Community Center. For more information, please call 850-891-3940. 801 Bragg Drive • Tallahassee, FL 32305 • Subscribe • Send an email • (850) 891-3942
